# Recommended CLAUDE.md Addition

Add these lines to your project's `CLAUDE.md` to activate the epistemic memory protocol:

```markdown
## Epistemic Memory

User profile beliefs are stored in the memory directory with per-belief confidence metadata.
Follow the protocol in `memory/user/epistemic-protocol.md` when updating beliefs:
- Only update beliefs actively relevant to the current session
- Confidence must be earned through evidence, not assigned by how insightful a belief sounds
- When observed behavior contradicts a belief, log a tension — don't silently resolve it
- Increment session counter at conversation start
- At periodic review thresholds, run `/mirror audit` or `/mirror gut-check`
```
